.modal-content
    .modal-header
        h3.modal-title Log into Linked Earth Wiki
    .modal-body
        p You must login to the Linked Earth Wiki before you can upload a file. If you're already logged in, click 'Upload' to skip the login.
    .modal-footer
        button(ng-if="data.button1" class="btn btn-success" data-dismiss="modal" ng-click="login()") Step 1: Log into Wiki
        button(ng-if="data.button2" class="btn btn-success" data-dismiss="modal" ng-click="upload()") Step 2: Upload LiPD file
        button(ng-if="data.button3" class="btn btn-primary" data-dismiss="modal" ng-click="close()") Close